{0 day11-opam}

Pure opam metadata helpers with no solver dependency.
{!Day11_opam.Git_packages} reads opam packages directly from git tree objects
without a working tree checkout, supporting both lazy and eager
loading, multi-repository layering, and inter-commit diffing.
{!Day11_opam.Git_utils} opens git stores and resolves commits and refs.
{!Day11_opam.Opam_env} provides the environment function for evaluating opam
filter expressions (arch, os, os-distribution, etc.).
This library has no dependency on the solver or the build system. It
sits near the bottom of the hierarchy, providing the package index
that the solver and build orchestration consume.

